Log:
  Implement the linprocfs swaps file, providing information about the
  configured swap devices in the Linux-compatible format.

  Based on the submission by:	Robert Millan <rmh debian org>
  PR:	kern/159281
  Reviewed by:	bde
  Approved by:	re (kensmith)
  MFC after:	2 weeks

